comments: Embiid (PHI) and Harris (PHI) are in the paint for about three seconds when they imminently exit.

Hampton (ORL) inadvertently dribbles the ball off of Harris' (PHI) foot as he moves alongside of him on the perimeter. There is judgement as to whether or not the foot to ball contact is intentional. Any contact as they come together during their pursuit of the loose ball is deemed incidental.
Harden (PHI) slightly extends his arm into Wagner (ORL), but the marginal contact does not affect his ability to receive the pass.
Bamba (ORL) brings his arm down and makes contact with Embiid (PHI), which dislodges him as he secures the rebound.
Harden (PHI) immediately slides his hand off of Carter Jr.'s (ORL) waist and marginal contact occurs as he disengages from the pick.
Before the block, Embiid (PHI) reaches in and makes contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) reaches for the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Bamba's (ORL) arm after his tip-shot attempt.
Harden (PHI) extends his arms and delivers contact to Carter Jr.'s (ORL) back while he is airborne, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
After the pick, Wagner (ORL) and Harris (PHI) mutually engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.

Carter (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position alongside Embiid (PHI), when Embiid loses control of the ball and it goes off of Carter Jr.'s (ORL) leg and out of bounds.  Possession correctly remains with PHI.
Wagner (ORL) jumps alongside of and absorbs the marginal contact created by Harris (ORL) during his play at the basket.
After Embiid's (PHI) missed tip-shot, Bamba (ORL) cleanly pokes the ball away during the rebound.
Harden (PHI) bats the rebound away from Hampton (ORL) and is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Embiid (PHI) lands off-balance after securing the rebound and falls to the floor before releasing his pass. Any contact with Carter Jr. (ORL) during the rebound is marginal.

Wagner (ORL) moves alongside of and absorbs the marginal contact created by Harden (PHI) during his driving shot attempt. Wagner removes his arm from Harden's (PHI) path and marginal contact occurs as Harden gathers the ball. Harden does not use his off-arm to overtly or abruptly clamp Wagner's arm.
Hampton (ORL) jumps up and extends his leg back to make contact with the ball and dislodge it from Embiid (PHI) out of bounds. A kicked ball violation should be called.
Carter Jr. (ORL) absorbs the contact from Niang (PHI) at the end of his drive and any follow-through contact to Niang's arm after he makes his intended pass is deemed incidental.
Harden's (PHI) jump shot bounces off of the rim and hits the top of the backboard and shot clock out of bounds. Orlando is correctly awarded possession of the ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Maxey's (PHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact during the pick.
Wagner (ORL) moves alongside of and absorbs the marginal contact created by Harden (PHI) during his driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Maxey's (PHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact during the pick.
Harris (PHI) rests his hand on Anthony's (ORL) side and marginal contact occurs before Embiid (PHI) cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) makes contact with Harden's (PHI) arm, which affects his ability to cleanly gather the ball and make his intended pass.
Wagner (ORL) and Embiid (PHI) mutually engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs as they jostle for post position.
Maxey (PHI) commits a take foul on Anthony (ORL).
Thybulle (PHI) reaches for the ball and marginal leg to leg contact occurs with Wagner (ORL) as Harden (PHI) simultaneously makes clean ball contact to temporarily dislodge it.

Replay review of the foul called on Thybulle (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Thybulle (PHI) cleanly block Anthony's (ORL) shot and any follow-through arm contact after the block is deemed incidental.
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Thybulle (PHI) reaches in and makes contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm, which affects his SQBR at the end of the drive.
Bamba (ORL) reaches in and makes contact with Harden's (PHI) arm before any clean ball contact by Carter Jr. (ORL) on his tie up attempt.
Thybulle (PHI) legally contests Anthony's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
